title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Lockheed Martin F 22A Raptor
description:
In this video we will look at version 1.0 of the Lockheed Martin F 22A Raptor. The Lockheed Martin F 22A Raptor is another fighter which you can add to your flight simulator install. If you like flying fighter this might be one you want to give a try.

If you also want to give the aircraft a try you can download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/16413/lockheed-martin-f-22a-raptor-top-mach-studios-freeware-edition
